These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, iced-tea, almond-milk, milk, lemonade, cola
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, canadian, nigerian, pakistani, russian, brazilian, indonesian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer, weightlifting, climbing, biathlon, badminton, rugby
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, trike, helicopter, car, skateboard, motorbike, bus
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the pakistani##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the indian is on the right of the indonesian##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the person driving the car is between the person driving the bus and the brazilian##2
 9. the russian is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking milk##1
12. the person drinking milk is the person driving the roller##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the nigerian##1
14. the brazilian is the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the indonesian##1
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
17. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the nigerian##1
18. the person drinking cola is on the right of the russian##1
19. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | lemonade        | milk | iced-tea      | almond-milk     | hot-chocolate      | cola     |
| Nationality   | canadian | pakistani         | indonesian   | indian | brazilian    | russian | nigerian |
